    "In instances, such as the above, the expertise of the researcher is required, to check the produced output (content) as well as cross-reference information from various sources.",
    "This is an important step to ensure that reliable, accurate, and trustworthy information is then used for the analysis process that may inform the formation of propositions and conceptualizations.",
